&lt;h2 id=&#34;optional&#34;&gt;(Optional)&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Although it&amp;rsquo;s far from the focus of the course,  we&amp;rsquo;ll be using the command-line in class, and you&amp;rsquo;ll be better off if you&amp;rsquo;re not trying to learn it from scratch alongside React.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&#34;command-line-power-user-by-wes-bos&#34;&gt;Command Line Power User by Wes Bos&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://commandlinepoweruser.com/&#34;&gt;Command Line Power User&lt;/a&gt; series by Wes Bos is an excellent introduction to the *NIX style command line. This free course requires an email sign up, but all the videos are on YouTube if you want to hunt for them. (Wes&amp;rsquo;s email list is pretty good though.)&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
